{"tid":1450540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T03:30:59.000Z","uid":21814,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"63a3e713c3f5b9d7d8c9fb334f33e984166b32c6","tid":1450540,"uid":21814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:41:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼</span></strong></span><br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，<span style=\"color: green;\">不是們的責任</span>，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n無時間做文宣<br />\n全世界幫手開Post推到全世界見到<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日 機場見</span>"},{"pid":"fac28621cfab990e5e6576def16cba977fe6fe6f","tid":1450540,"uid":21814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:55:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"3ba083b26fc02fd2c828874022e78ff398041e0d","tid":1450540,"uid":21814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:55:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />機場要人"},{"pid":"92fa3fb402f1762d9cc58078af896a3716d48fe3","tid":1450540,"uid":21814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:56:02.000Z","msg":"無人可以習慣呢種壓迫"},{"pid":"073c5ce0eb999e723a9f5e753b5054ef05af2226","tid":1450540,"uid":21814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:56:37.000Z","msg":"最後一淡氣都同你死過"},{"pid":"8adcf210a1ef5743c79e98e4b15e2226daa8cc9f","tid